#. <section class="sutta" id="an3.83"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an3.83:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 3"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 3"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.83:0.2"
msgid "9. Samaṇavagga"
msgstr "9. Ascetics"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an3.83:0.3"
msgid "83. Khettasutta"
msgstr "83. Fields"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pli1.230"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an3.83:1.1"
msgid "“Tīṇimāni, bhikkhave, kassakassa gahapatissa pubbe karaṇīyāni."
msgstr "“Mendicants, a farmer has three primary duties."

msgctxt "an3.83:1.2"
msgid "Katamāni tīṇi?"
msgstr "What three?"

#. VAR: paṭikacceva → paṭigacceva (bj, pts1)
#. VAR: sumatikataṃ → sumattikataṃ (mr)
msgctxt "an3.83:1.3"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, kassako gahapati paṭikacceva khettaṃ sukaṭṭhaṃ karoti "
"sumatikataṃ."
msgstr "A farmer first of all makes sure the field is well ploughed and tilled."

msgctxt "an3.83:1.4"
msgid ""
"Paṭikacceva khettaṃ sukaṭṭhaṃ karitvā sumatikataṃ kālena bījāni patiṭṭhāpeti."
msgstr "Next they plant seeds in season."

msgctxt "an3.83:1.5"
msgid "Kālena bījāni patiṭṭhāpetvā samayena udakaṃ abhinetipi apanetipi."
msgstr "When the time is right, they irrigate the field and then drain it."

msgctxt "an3.83:1.6"
msgid "Imāni kho, bhikkhave, tīṇi kassakassa gahapatissa pubbe karaṇīyāni."
msgstr "These are the three primary duties of a farmer."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an3.83:2.1"
msgid "Evamevaṃ kho, bhikkhave, tīṇimāni bhikkhussa pubbe karaṇīyāni."
msgstr "In the same way, a mendicant has three primary duties."

msgctxt "an3.83:2.2"
msgid "Katamāni tīṇi?"
msgstr "What three?"

msgctxt "an3.83:2.3"
msgid ""
"Adhisīlasikkhāsamādānaṃ, adhicittasikkhāsamādānaṃ, adhipaññāsikkhāsamādānaṃ—"
msgstr ""
"Undertaking the training in the higher ethics, the higher mind, and the "
"higher wisdom."

msgctxt "an3.83:2.4"
msgid "imāni kho, bhikkhave, tīṇi bhikkhussa pubbe karaṇīyāni."
msgstr "These are the three primary duties of a mendicant."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an3.83:3.1"
msgid "Tasmātiha, bhikkhave, evaṃ sikkhitabbaṃ:"
msgstr "So you should train like this:"

msgctxt "an3.83:3.2"
msgid ""
"‘tibbo no chando bhavissati adhisīlasikkhāsamādāne, tibbo no chando "
"bhavissati adhicittasikkhāsamādāne, tibbo no chando bhavissati "
"adhipaññāsikkhāsamādāne’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘We will have keen enthusiasm for undertaking the training in the higher "
"ethics, the higher mind, and the higher wisdom.’"

msgctxt "an3.83:3.3"
msgid "Evañhi vo, bhikkhave, sikkhitabban”ti."
msgstr "That’s how you should train.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an3.83:3.4"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
